Photo of Island Travel & Tours Ltd, President, William J. Hauf, Congratulating Jeffrey DeLaurentis upon today’s opening of the U.S. Embassy in Cuba Available on Business Wire's Website and AP PhotoExpress 
Island Travel & Tours Ltd, President, William J. Hauf, Congratulates Jeffrey DeLaurentis upon today’s opening of the U.S. Embassy in Cuba, after a 54 Year Hiatus, and his appointment as the “Senior Most Official” at the Embassy. Download
